<div class="trpHomePanel" id="chat-frame">
  <div class="trpHomeContainer" id="content-frame">
  
    {{#if prettyWelcome}} 

    <div class="prettyWelcome"> 
      <h1>Welcome to Gitter!</h1>

      <h2>What's next?</h2>
      <p>Chat and receive notifications on the go. We also have an IRC bridge and an API.</p>
      <div class='features'>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="http://update.gitter.im/osx/latest" target="_blank">Mac</a></li>
          <li><a href="http://appstore.com/gitter" target="_blank">iOS</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://irc.gitter.im" target="_blank">IRC</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://developer.gitter.im/docs/welcome" target="_blank">API</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <p><small>Android, Linux and Windows coming soon.</small></p>

      <h2>Talk To Us</h2>
      <p>We hang out in <a href='https://gitter.im/gitterhq/gitter' target="_blank">#gitterhq/gitter</a> and would love to hear from you. You can also follow <a href="https://twitter.com/gitchat">@gitchat</a> on Twitter for the latest news.</p>

      <h2>Discover Features</h2>
      <p>Level up your skills: keyboard shortcuts, /commands, file sharing, and other tricks. <a href="https://gitter.zendesk.com/hc/en-us" target="_blank">Learn more &rarr;</a></p>

      <h2>Explore Communities</h2>
      <p>We host thousands of open source communities and user groups. <a href='/explore' target="_blank">Explore &rarr;</a></p>

      <h2>Gitter Data Liberation Front</h2>
      <p>Content generated in public rooms is licensed under Creative Commons BY-NC-SA. Export messages easily using the <a href="https://developer.gitter.im" target="_blank">API</a>.</p>
    </div>

    {{else}}

    <div class="trpHomeLogo"></div>
    <br>
    <br>
    <br>

    <h2>YOUR ORGANIZATIONS</h2>
    <div id="org-list"></div>

    <h2>SUGGESTED ROOMS</h2>
    {{#if showUpgradeAuthLink}}
    <div class="banner-red">
      <a id="upgrade-auth" style="color: white" href="/login/upgrade?scopes=repo" target="_new">
        Want to see your private repositories? Click here to Authorise with GitHub
      </a>.
    </div>
    {{/if}}
    <div id="suggested-room-list"></div>

    {{/if}}

  </div>
</div>
